      • OpenHashSet

        public OpenHashSet(java.lang.String[] data)
        Data constructor - builds the hash set by adding the elements one by one. Duplicate values should be ignored. The new table has the default values of initial capacity (16), upper load factor (0.75), and lower load factor (0.25).
        Parameters:
        data - Values to add to the set.
